  "rationale": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice A is correct. The area of a square is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"s squared\"><msup><mi>s</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>, where <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"s\"><mi>s</mi></math> is the side length of the square. Therefore, the area of square B is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"b squared\"><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>, where&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"b\"><mi>b</mi></math> is the side length of square B. It&rsquo;s given that square A has side lengths that are <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"246\"><mn>246</mn></math> times the side lengths of square B. Therefore, the side length of square A can be represented by the expression <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"246 b\"><mn>246</mn><mi>b</mi></math>. It follows that the area of square A is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"left parenthesis 246 b right parenthesis squared\"><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>246</mn><mi>b</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></math>, or <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"60,516 b squared\"><mn>60,516</mn><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>. It&rsquo;s given that the area of square A is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"k\"><mi>k</mi></math> times the area of square B, so&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"60,516 b squared equals k b squared\"><mn>60,516</mn><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mi>k</mi><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>. Therefore, the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"k\"><mi>k</mi></math> is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"60,516\"><mn>60,516</mn></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice B is incorrect and may result from conceptual or calculation errors.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice C is incorrect and may result from conceptual or calculation errors.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice D is incorrect and may result from conceptual or calculation errors.</p>",
